\c 20
\s Amanzi akhutshwa edwaleni
\p
\v 1 Khona abantwana bakoIsrayeli, inhlangano yonke, bafika enkangala yeZini ngenyanga yokuqala; labantu bahlala eKadeshi\x + 33.36.Nani 13.21.\x*. UMiriyamu wasefela lapho, wangcwatshwa khona\x + Eks. 15.20. Nani 12.1; 26.59.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo kwakungelamanzi enhlangano\x + Eks. 17.1.\x*; ngakho bahlangana bamelana loMozisi bamelana loAroni\x + 16.19,42.\x*.
\v 3 Abantu baphikisana loMozisi bakhuluma besithi: Kungathi ngabe safa\x + Eks. 17.2; Nani 14.2.\x* ekufeni kwabafowethu phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 11.1,33; 14.37; 16.32,35,49.\x*\nd*!
\v 4 Liletheleni ibandla leN\nd kosi\nd* enkangala le ukuze sifele lapha, thina lezifuyo zethu?\x + Eks. 17.3.\x*
\v 5 Lasenyuselani sisuka eGibhithe ukusiletha kulindawo embi? Kakusiyo indawo yenhlanyelo lemikhiwa lamavini \w lamapomegranati\w**, futhi kakulamanzi okunatha.
\v 6 UMozisi loAroni basebesuka phambi kwebandla, baya emnyango wethente lenhlangano, bathi mbo ngobuso babo phansi\x + 14.5; 16.4,22,45.\x*. Inkazimulo yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasibonakala kubo\x + 14.10.\x*.
\p
\v 7 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 8 Thatha intonga, ubuthanise inhlangano, wena loAroni umnewenu, likhulume kulo idwala phambi kwamehlo abo, njalo lizanika amanzi alo\x + Eks. 17.5.\x*; ngalokhu uzabakhuphela amanzi edwaleni, ukuze ulinathise ibandla lezifuyo zabo\x + Neh. 9.15. Isa. 43.20; 48.21.\x*.
\v 9 UMozisi wasethatha intonga esuka phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* njengokumlaya kwayo\x + 17.10.\x*.
\v 10 UMozisi loAroni basebebuthanisa ibandla phambi kwedwala; wasesithi kubo: Zwanini-ke, lina bahlamuki; sizalikhuphela yini amanzi edwaleni leli?\x + Hlab. 106.32,33.\x*
\v 11 UMozisi wasephakamisa isandla sakhe, watshaya idwala kabili ngentonga yakhe; kwasekumpompoza amanzi amanengi, inhlangano yasinatha, lezifuyo zayo\x + Dute. 8.15. Eks. 17.6.\x*.
\p
\v 12 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi lakuAroni: Ngoba lingangikholwanga\x + 27.14. Dute. 1.37; 3.26; 32.51.\x*, ukungingcwelisa emehlweni abantwana bakoIsrayeli, ngakho kaliyikungenisa ibandla leli elizweni engibanike lona\x + Hez. 20.41; 36.23; 38.16.\x*.
\v 13 La ngamanzi eMeriba, lapho abantwana bakoIsrayeli abaphikisana khona leN\nd kosi\nd*, yasingcweliswa kubo\x + Dute. 33.8. Hlab. 81.7; 95.8; 106.32.\x*.
\s Inkosi yeEdoma ivalela abantwana bakoIsrayeli indlela
\p
\v 14 UMozisi wasethuma izithunywa enkosini yeEdoma\x + Gen. 36.39.\x* zisuka eKadeshi \add wathi\x + Hlu. 11.16,17.\x*\add*: Utsho njalo umfowenu uIsrayeli: Wena uyazazi zonke inkathazo ezisehleleyo\x + Dute. 2.4-6; 23.7. Obad. 10,12.\x*,
\v 15 lokuthi obaba behlela eGibhithe\x + Gen. 46.6. Seb. 7.15.\x*, sasesihlala eGibhithe insuku ezinengi\x + Eks. 12.40.\x*; lamaGibhithe asiphatha kubi labobaba\x + Dute. 26.6. Eks. 1.11; Seb. 7.19.\x*.
\v 16 Sasesikhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, yasisizwa ilizwi lethu\x + Eks. 2.23; 3.7.\x*, yathuma ingilosi, yasikhupha eGibhithe; khangela-ke siseKadeshi, umuzi osekucineni komngcele wakho\x + Eks. 3.2; 14.19; 23.20; 33.2.\x*.
\v 17 Ake usiyekele sidabule elizweni lakho. Kasiyikudabula ensimini loba esivinini, futhi kasiyikunatha amanzi omthombo. Sizahamba ngomgwaqo wenkosi, kasiyikuphambukela ngakwesokunene langakwesokhohlo, size sedlule umngcele wakho\x + 21.22. Dute. 2.27.\x*.
\v 18 Kodwa uEdoma wathi kuye: Kawuyikudabula kimi, hlezi ngiphume ngenkemba ngimelane lawe.
\v 19 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesithi kuye: Sizahamba ngomgwaqo omkhulu. Uba-ke mina lezifuyo zami sinatha okwamanzi akho\x + 2 Sam. 20.12,13. Isa. 11.16; 19.23.\x*, sizawabhadalela\x + Dute. 2.6,28.\x*; kuphela ngizadabula ngenyawo zami nje.
\v 20 Kodwa wathi: Kawuyikudabula. UEdoma wasephuma wamelana laye elabantu abanengi, langesandla esilamandla.
\v 21 Ngalokhu uEdoma wala ukuvumela uIsrayeli ukudabula emngceleni wakhe\x + Dute. 2.29.\x*. Ngakho uIsrayeli waphambuka wasuka kuye\x + 21.4. Dute. 2.8. Hlu. 11.18.\x*.
\s Ukufa kukaAroni entabeni yeHori
\p
\v 22 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli, inhlangano yonke, basebesuka eKadeshi\x + 33.37.\x*, bafika entabeni yeHori\x + 21.4.\x*.
\v 23 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi lakuAroni entabeni yeHori, emngceleni welizwe leEdoma, isithi:
\v 24 UAroni uzabuthelwa ebantwini bakibo, ngoba kayikungena elizweni engilinike abantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 27.13; 31.2. Dute. 32.50,26. Gen. 25.8.\x*, ngoba lahlamukela ilizwi lami emanzini eMeriba\x + 20.12.\x*.
\v 25 Thatha uAroni loEleyazare indodana yakhe, ubenyusele entabeni yeHori,
\v 26 umhlubule uAroni izembatho zakhe, uzifake kuEleyazare indodana yakhe; ngoba uAroni uzabuthelwa \add kwabakibo\add*, afele lapho\x + 20.24.\x*.
\v 27 UMozisi wenza njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd*. Basebesenyukela entabeni yeHori phambi kwamehlo enhlangano yonke.
\v 28 UMozisi wasemhlubula uAroni izembatho zakhe, wazifaka kuEleyazare indodana yakhe\x + Eks. 29.29,30.\x*. UAroni wasefela lapho engqongeni yentaba. UMozisi loEleyazare basebesehla entabeni\x + Dute. 10.6; Dute. 32.50.33.38.\x*.
\v 29 Lapho inhlangano yonke ibona ukuthi uAroni usephelile, balilela uAroni insuku ezingamatshumi amathathu, indlu yonke kaIsrayeli\x + Dute. 34.8. Gen. 50.3.\x*.